people who really need it.

00:02:20.500 --> 00:02:22.440
And I was surprised when
we began this project

00:02:22.440 --> 00:02:23.970
to learn that there
has never been

00:02:23.970 --> 00:02:26.840
a major survey of the seriously
ill people who use the health

00:02:26.840 --> 00:02:28.650
care system the most.

00:02:28.650 --> 00:02:31.200
