the Commonwealth Fund

00:02:31.200 --> 00:02:35.480
and the Harvard School of Public
Health, we surveyed nearly 14--

00:02:35.480 --> 00:02:39.030
sorry, we surveyed
1,495 people who

00:02:39.030 --> 00:02:41.430
had real health problems,
multiple hospitalizations

00:02:41.430 --> 00:02:44.790
and doctor's visits, and often
many other needs besides.

00:02:44.790 --> 00:02:47.645
