00:40:54.750 --> 00:40:56.910
financial costs and
different reimbursements that

00:40:56.910 --> 00:40:57.837
can go with that?

00:41:01.975 --> 00:41:04.300
TOYIN AJAYI: Bob,
you have to start.

00:41:04.300 --> 00:41:06.759
ROBERT MASTER: I was going to
