interdisciplinary
care teams, all

00:52:05.290 --> 00:52:08.677
of the principles that we
bring to the work that we do

00:52:08.677 --> 00:52:10.510
have had a chance to
be baked and germinated

00:52:10.510 --> 00:52:11.759
through an innovation process.

00:52:11.759 --> 00:52:14.500
And it is a remarkable
moment in time

00:52:14.500 --> 00:52:18.230
when we can say collectively as
a community, we have a problem.

00:52:18.230 --> 00:52:21.400
And this problem is both
access and the quality of care

00:52:21.400 --> 00:52:23.390
that we provide to people
